{
  "texts": [
    "Their technique enhances the defect fixing performance by applying transfer learning techniques.",
    "Tian et al. [610] proposed BATS, a learning-based model designed to predict the correctness of patches.",
    "BATS is an unsupervised model that repairs faulty programs by detecting program behavior during failed test cases.",
    "Yuan et al. [611] proposed CIRCLE, a T5-based model for patch generation.",
    "CIRCLE employs continual learning techniques and is able to work on multiple programming languages."
  ]
}